<i>noun</i>: 구속복 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>구속복</dt><br>
<dd>a garment similar to a jacket that is used to bind the arms tightly against the body as a means of restraining a violent person</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: straitjacket, straightjacket</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
